(1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'Site', '<p>Here you can update the site related settings.</p>\r\n<p>You can update the informations like Site Name, Site Default City, Site Routing URL, Site Currency, Site language.</p>\r\n<p>You can also change the PayPal currency code here. To know more about PayPal supported currency codes visit <a target="_blank" href="https://cms.paypal.com/us/cgi-bin/?cmd=_render-content&content_ID=developer/e_howto_api_nvp_currency_codes">PayPal Currency Codes</a>'),
